headfirst.

411
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:00,000
Don't mistake jerks
for good guys.

412
00:18:01,241 --> 00:18:02,361
Don't say I don't treat you well.

413
00:18:02,401 --> 00:18:04,041
I'm giving you a chance
to return a favor,

414
00:18:04,081 --> 00:18:05,281
