427
00:18:39,921 --> 00:18:40,641
No.

428
00:18:40,681 --> 00:18:41,481
I don't want peace.

429
00:18:47,001 --> 00:18:48,601
When you eat with Wen Cheng,

430
00:18:48,641 --> 00:18:49,881
