431
00:18:50,321 --> 00:18:51,321
I'm free anyway.

432
00:19:07,521 --> 00:19:08,161
Waiter.

433
00:19:08,681 --> 00:19:09,241
Coffee.

434
00:19:12,681 --> 00:19:13,241
Old Jiang.

435
00:19:14,001 --> 00:19:14,561
Why are you looking for me?

436
00:19:15,641 --> 00:19:17,041
If you want to mess around,
find someone else.

437
00:19:17,081 --> 00:19:18,001
Don't bother Yao Yuan.

438
00:19:19,081 --> 00:19:20,441
Who says I'm messing around?

439
00:19:21,041 --> 00:19:21,721
