no matter what.

533
00:23:42,281 --> 00:23:42,681
Okay.

534
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:43,680
I'll listen to you.

535
00:24:00,961 --> 00:24:02,001
Because of what she said,

536
00:24:02,801 --> 00:24:04,201
