540
00:24:10,681 --> 00:24:11,441
But Yao Yuan—

541
00:24:11,681 --> 00:24:12,721
She was the campus beauty.

542
00:24:12,761 --> 00:24:14,601
She was genuinely kind to everyone.

543
00:24:15,081 --> 00:24:16,241
At that time, I thought,

544
00:24:16,521 --> 00:24:17,441
I told myself I had to become

545
00:24:17,481 --> 00:24:18,681
