549
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,920
Sounds like you peaked early, huh?

550
00:24:38,961 --> 00:24:39,681
Hey, Jiang.

551
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:41,960
Listen,

552
00:24:42,561 --> 00:24:44,521
You lacked confidence back then,

553
00:24:44,561 --> 00:24:45,601
