563
00:25:14,961 --> 00:25:16,881
But you’re in college now.

564
00:25:16,921 --> 00:25:18,841
You should enjoy campus life.

565
00:25:18,881 --> 00:25:20,441
Don’t put too much pressure on yourself.

566
00:25:20,961 --> 00:25:22,241
Got it, sis.

567
00:25:24,041 --> 00:25:25,801
Hi, Yao Yuan. I’m Zhang Jie.

