00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:30,480
After class today,

571
00:25:30,521 --> 00:25:31,441
are you free?

572
00:25:31,481 --> 00:25:32,521
I’d like to take you to a movie.

573
00:25:33,001 --> 00:25:35,001
You’re trying to date our Yao Yuan, huh?

574
00:25:35,360 --> 00:25:35,880
Yes.

575
00:25:35,921 --> 00:25:36,841
Which department are you in?

576
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:37,840
Medical department.

577
00:25:38,921 --> 00:25:40,161
No bad habits.

578
00:25:40,201 --> 00:25:41,841
Likes basketball and playing violin.

579
00:25:43,241 --> 00:25:45,481
How about giving him a chance?

580
00:25:49,521 --> 00:25:50,201
Classmate,

581
00:25:50,961 --> 00:25:51,801
Sorry,

582
00:25:52,081 --> 00:25:54,441
I don’t want to date for a few years.

583
00:25:54,481 --> 00:25:55,801
Besides studying,

584
00:25:55,841 --> 00:25:57,961
I want to focus on other things.

585
00:25:59,001 --> 00:26:00,401
You’re great, really outstanding.

586
00:26:01,001 --> 00:26:02,241
But no matter who it is,

587
00:26:02,681 --> 00:26:03,881
I wouldn’t accept.

588
00:26:04,521 --> 00:26:05,401
Sorry.

589
00:26:06,841 --> 00:26:07,401
Alright.

590
00:26:17,801 --> 00:26:19,001
Later, I went to the US.

591
00:26:19,601 --> 00:26:20,721
I thought, after a while,

592
00:26:20,761 --> 00:26:22,121
everyone would meet new people.

593
00:26:22,921 --> 00:26:23,961
But I didn’t expect

594
00:26:58,321 --> 00:26:59,641
when I saw her again,

595
00:27:00,681 --> 00:27:01,801
I just knew

596
00:27:01,841 --> 00:27:03,361
she was the one I’d been looking for.

597
00:27:05,601 --> 00:27:06,921
So fate brought us together again

598
00:27:06,961 --> 00:27:08,161
for a reason.

599
00:27:09,360 --> 00:27:10,160
This time,

600
00:27:10,521 --> 00:27:12,001
I worked so hard to find her.

601
00:27:12,641 --> 00:27:14,081
Tried to enter her world.

602
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:15,200
Just so I wouldn’t miss her again.

603
00:27:15,241 --> 00:27:16,721
I won’t let myself miss her again.

604
00:27:18,561 --> 00:27:19,161
I get it.

605
00:27:20,721 --> 00:27:21,321
I surrender.

606
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:22,680
No,

607
00:27:24,961 --> 00:27:26,041
You went through so much

608
00:27:26,081 --> 00:27:27,201
before falling for her.

609
00:27:27,561 --> 00:27:28,881
I liked her at second sight.

610
00:27:29,721 --> 00:27:30,761
So I think

611
00:27:31,321 --> 00:27:31,961
I won’t lose.

612
00:27:32,761 --> 00:27:33,841
Because I’m sincere too.

613
00:27:34,841 --> 00:27:36,841
You’re really confident in yourself.

614
00:27:38,001 --> 00:27:38,841
Yao Yuan truly is

615
00:27:38,881 --> 00:27:40,201
a rare, wonderful girl.

616
00:27:40,721 --> 00:27:41,241
Mm-hmm.

617
00:27:41,961 --> 00:27:43,041
So, Jiang,

618
00:27:43,081 --> 00:27:45,041
stop telling me to give up on her, okay?

619
00:27:45,081 --> 00:27:46,281
She’s not just some shirt,

620
00:27:46,321 --> 00:27:47,201
or a job.

621
00:27:47,721 --> 00:27:49,041
She’s my new goal.

622
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:50,480
I can become better for her.

623
00:27:52,041 --> 00:27:53,201
I admire your courage.

624
00:27:53,761 --> 00:27:54,681
But you can’t beat me.

625
00:27:55,241 --> 00:27:56,801
Yao Yuan’s heart has long been mine.

626
00:28:00,041 --> 00:28:02,281
Love is full of surprises.

627
00:28:02,841 --> 00:28:04,001
Until the end,

628
00:28:04,761 --> 00:28:05,761
no one knows who’ll win.

629
00:28:06,481 --> 00:28:08,361
Failure isn’t allowed in my world.

630
00:28:08,801 --> 00:28:10,361
That’s your world.

631
00:28:10,401 --> 00:28:12,961
Others can be indecisive in their world.

632
00:28:13,241 --> 00:28:14,881
Yao Yuan isn’t like that.

633
00:28:14,921 --> 00:28:16,241
That’s because she hasn’t met me yet.

634
00:28:23,721 --> 00:28:24,281
Jiang,

635
00:28:25,801 --> 00:28:27,881
I know you always win.

636
00:28:28,841 --> 00:28:29,761
But—

637
00:28:29,801 --> 00:28:32,121
Your reaction to my challenge

638
00:28:32,881 --> 00:28:33,961
makes me think

639
00:28:34,881 --> 00:28:36,081
maybe you have a bit of

640
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:37,480
uncertainty inside.

641
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,160
Although

642
00:28:44,201 --> 00:28:45,521
I don’t know what it is either.

643
00:28:54,041 --> 00:28:54,641
Jiang,

644
00:28:55,921 --> 00:28:57,081
let’s compete fairly.

645
00:29:00,001 --> 00:29:01,521
Love can’t tolerate any impurity.

646
00:29:02,321 --> 00:29:03,041
I can’t promise

647
00:29:03,081 --> 00:29:04,641
our rivalry will be gentlemanly.

648
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:08,001
I can’t promise that either.

649
00:29:13,601 --> 00:29:14,161
Hold on.

650
00:29:26,881 --> 00:29:28,921
Why does he look so good today?

651
00:29:29,801 --> 00:29:32,441
Is it the color of his clothes or his hair?

652
00:29:37,681 --> 00:29:39,561
Her outfit fits better than usual today.

653
00:29:40,441 --> 00:29:42,001
Or are her heels one centimeter higher?

654
00:29:43,161 --> 00:29:45,201
Her legs look extra long.

655
00:29:53,521 --> 00:29:54,281
Apple martini.

656
00:29:54,561 --> 00:29:55,321
I remember you like it.

657
00:29:56,081 --> 00:29:57,441
You offer me a drink right away.

658
00:29:57,481 --> 00:29:58,561
What’s your motive?

659
00:29:58,601 --> 00:30:00,201
Didn’t want you to wait, so I ordered first.

660
00:30:01,041 --> 00:30:02,241
You’re so guarded.

661
00:30:13,001 --> 00:30:14,081
What a coincidence.

662
00:30:14,121 --> 00:30:15,081
You’re here too?

663
00:30:15,121 --> 00:30:16,441
Weren’t you looking for me?

664
00:30:17,401 --> 00:30:18,321
Was I?

665
00:30:18,361 --> 00:30:19,641
I was just passing by.

666
00:30:20,481 --> 00:30:21,761
Since you’re here, join us.

667
00:30:21,801 --> 00:30:22,721
Mm, okay.

668
00:30:28,281 --> 00:30:30,121
You always put romance before friends.

669
00:30:34,761 --> 00:30:35,241
Wen Cheng,

670
00:30:37,041 --> 00:30:37,721
today,

671
00:30:37,961 --> 00:30:38,921
you look really handsome.

672
00:30:40,241 --> 00:30:41,401
Aren’t I always this handsome?

673
00:30:42,121 --> 00:30:43,681
I ordered food first, hope you don’t mind.

674
00:30:44,681 --> 00:30:45,521
Of course not.

675
00:30:45,921 --> 00:30:46,761
I like

676
00:30:46,801 --> 00:30:48,401
guys who always think of girls first.

677
00:30:50,041 --> 00:30:50,441
Let’s eat.

678
00:30:59,081 --> 00:30:59,601
Your favorite food.

679
00:31:00,481 --> 00:31:01,001
Thank you.

680
00:31:01,881 --> 00:31:02,761
Xinran.

681
00:31:03,281 --> 00:31:04,521
Wen Cheng treats you so well.

682
00:31:05,601 --> 00:31:07,281
He just needs something from me.

683
00:31:07,721 --> 00:31:08,601
By the way, Wen Cheng—

684
00:31:08,641 --> 00:31:09,521
Go ahead, what do you want?

685
00:31:10,841 --> 00:31:11,361
Okay.

686
00:31:11,761 --> 00:31:14,121
I need to prep the outline before the show.

687
00:31:14,161 --> 00:31:15,761
I want to formally ask you a few questions.

688
00:31:16,521 --> 00:31:18,081
Someone as attractive as you,

689
00:31:18,121 --> 00:31:20,241
who’s also independent in life—

690
00:31:20,601 --> 00:31:22,521
what do you think are the pros and cons of blind dates?

691
00:31:23,521 --> 00:31:24,561
When it comes to blind dates,

692
00:31:24,601 --> 00:31:25,721
you’re asking the right person.

693
00:31:25,921 --> 00:31:27,401
I’m a blind date expert.

694
00:31:27,441 --> 00:31:30,161
I’ve met all types—tall, short, oddballs.

695
00:31:30,561 --> 00:31:31,401
But still,

696
00:31:32,361 --> 00:31:34,201
none as high-quality as you.

697
00:31:35,641 --> 00:31:37,081
Xiaoya, you’re so honest.

698
00:31:37,601 --> 00:31:39,921
I’m just afraid if I go, everyone will pick me.

699
00:31:39,961 --> 00:31:41,761
Wouldn’t that ruin other guys’ happiness?

700
00:31:42,481 --> 00:31:43,161
So,

701
00:31:43,361 --> 00:31:44,441
I give up automatically.

702
00:31:44,481 --> 00:31:45,721
Let others have a chance.

703
00:31:47,681 --> 00:31:49,841
You go on blind dates to find true love.

704
00:31:50,561 --> 00:31:52,361
If not for true love, what else?

705
00:31:52,401 --> 00:31:53,601
Find a roommate?

706
00:31:54,121 --> 00:31:55,281
There are many ways to fall in love.

707
00:31:55,321 --> 00:31:56,521
Why must it be blind dates?

708
00:31:57,161 --> 00:31:59,321
Society values efficiency now.

709
00:31:59,361 --> 00:32:00,761
Blind dates are like job interviews.

710
00:32:00,801 --> 00:32:02,041
If it’s not a match, just delete.

711
00:32:02,401 --> 00:32:03,281
No time wasted,

712
00:32:03,321 --> 00:32:04,761
no stress about rejecting people.

713
00:32:06,001 --> 00:32:07,521
Didn’t you oppose blind dates before?

714
00:32:08,121 --> 00:32:09,161
Why are you so talkative now?

715
00:32:10,041 --> 00:32:11,121
Can’t I be flexible?

716
00:32:12,161 --> 00:32:13,561
I’m not like Xinran.

717
00:32:15,401 --> 00:32:16,601
I believe

718
00:32:16,641 --> 00:32:18,321
my true love is truly lost.

719
00:32:18,721 --> 00:32:19,841
So I have to

720
00:32:19,881 --> 00:32:21,401
search through the crowd.

721
00:32:22,001 --> 00:32:22,281
Him.

722
00:32:24,001 --> 00:32:24,801
Don’t you think

723
00:32:24,841 --> 00:32:26,601
blind dates are just two lonely people

724
00:32:26,641 --> 00:32:27,721
trying to comfort each other?

725
00:32:28,721 --> 00:32:29,521
Maybe so.

726
00:32:30,041 --> 00:32:30,681
But

727
00:32:30,721 --> 00:32:32,601
what woman doesn’t want a good home?

728
00:32:33,321 --> 00:32:34,641
Doesn’t want to be cared for?

729
00:32:36,961 --> 00:32:38,801
But I’ve realized,

730
00:32:39,721 --> 00:32:41,401
fate is right beside me.

731
00:32:42,321 --> 00:32:43,001
Ah.

732
00:32:44,161 --> 00:32:45,041
Before,

733
00:32:45,321 --> 00:32:46,641
I always messed around with Baihua Tang and you.

734
00:32:47,121 --> 00:32:48,521
Looking back, that was silly.

735
00:32:48,801 --> 00:32:50,321
You’re so handsome yourself.

736
00:32:51,161 --> 00:32:52,761
Why did I always look elsewhere?

737
00:32:53,201 --> 00:32:54,321
Why not look in Tianxia Bang?

738
00:32:55,641 --> 00:32:56,921
Xiaoya, cheers to you.

739
00:33:00,681 --> 00:33:01,481
Speaking of Tianxia Bang,

740
00:33:01,681 --> 00:33:02,681
have you played games lately?

741
00:33:03,841 --> 00:33:04,601
I think

742
00:33:04,641 --> 00:33:06,481
we could grind dungeons together.

743
00:33:06,921 --> 00:33:08,001
Sure, I’ll heal you.

744
00:33:10,521 --> 00:33:12,481
It’s still early.

745
00:33:12,521 --> 00:33:13,281
How about

746
00:33:13,321 --> 00:33:14,681
we go somewhere else for another drink?

747
00:33:15,001 --> 00:33:15,841
You’re already this drunk,

748
00:33:15,881 --> 00:33:16,681
and still want more?

749
00:33:16,921 --> 00:33:17,561
Let’s go, let’s go.

750
00:33:23,721 --> 00:33:24,961
The weather changes so fast.

751
00:33:25,481 --> 00:33:26,201
It’s freezing!

752
00:33:30,641 --> 00:33:31,281
Put this on.

753
00:33:31,321 --> 00:33:32,121
Don’t catch a cold.

754
00:33:34,641 --> 00:33:36,281
Xinran, thank you.

755
00:33:39,641 --> 00:33:40,321
Ah.

756
00:33:40,361 --> 00:33:41,401
Look at me, so forgetful.

757
00:33:41,441 --> 00:33:42,521
I forgot I need to take Yao Xinran

758
00:33:42,561 --> 00:33:44,241
to our company for a show rehearsal.

759
00:33:44,641 --> 00:33:45,041
Xiaoya.

760
00:33:45,081 --> 00:33:45,841
Let’s drink next time.

761
00:33:46,721 --> 00:33:47,601
Ah.

762
00:33:48,841 --> 00:33:50,001
A rehearsal this late?

763
00:33:54,281 --> 00:33:54,841
Xiaoya.

764
00:33:55,001 --> 00:33:56,001
Then you head home first.

765
00:33:56,041 --> 00:33:56,921
Be careful, okay?

766
00:33:57,641 --> 00:33:58,401
But—

767
00:33:58,441 --> 00:34:00,161
I want to go to the production company too.

768
00:34:00,201 --> 00:34:01,721
Since I was little,

769
00:34:01,761 --> 00:34:02,881
I’ve never been.

770
00:34:03,881 --> 00:34:04,401
Xiaoya.

771
00:34:04,441 --> 00:34:05,401
It’s not that I won’t let you go.

772
00:34:05,441 --> 00:34:06,041
It’s just

773
00:34:06,081 --> 00:34:08,281
unreleased content must stay secret.

774
00:34:08,720 --> 00:34:10,160
Unrelated people are kept out.

775
00:34:11,201 --> 00:34:11,721
I see.

776
00:34:12,961 --> 00:34:14,441
Alright then.

777
00:34:14,481 --> 00:34:15,641
I’ll head home now.

778
00:34:16,681 --> 00:34:18,001
You should go home early too.

779
00:34:18,041 --> 00:34:19,401
It’s cold and dark outside.

780
00:34:21,881 --> 00:34:22,641
Next time,

781
00:34:22,681 --> 00:34:23,561
we must drink together.

782
00:34:24,041 --> 00:34:24,561
Definitely.

783
00:34:27,001 --> 00:34:27,401
Bye.

784
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:28,200
Bye.

785
00:34:28,841 --> 00:34:29,921
Take care.

786
00:34:29,961 --> 00:34:30,921
Call me when you get home.

787
00:34:34,041 --> 00:34:34,921
Wen Cheng.

788
00:34:34,961 --> 00:34:36,401
What are you up to?

789
00:34:36,441 --> 00:34:37,801
You’re the one up to something.

790
00:34:38,041 --> 00:34:39,081
What’s up with Li Xiaoya?

791
00:34:39,121 --> 00:34:40,081
Possessed by Pikachu.

792
00:34:40,121 --> 00:34:41,041
Sparking nonstop.

793
00:34:41,081 --> 00:34:42,201
How are you not fried yet?

794
00:34:42,761 --> 00:34:43,321
No,

795
00:34:43,361 --> 00:34:44,161
I’m really scared of

796
00:34:44,201 --> 00:34:45,481
women with love deficiency syndrome.

797
00:34:46,041 --> 00:34:47,881
Desperate for male hormones.

798
00:34:47,921 --> 00:34:49,281
Don’t talk about her like that.

799
00:34:49,321 --> 00:34:50,601
Everyone wants to fall in love.

800
00:35:01,921 --> 00:35:02,361
Let’s go.

801
00:35:02,921 --> 00:35:03,481
Where do you live?

802
00:35:03,521 --> 00:35:04,081
I’ll walk you home.

803
00:35:05,001 --> 00:35:05,641
No need.

804
00:35:05,681 --> 00:35:06,721
I can get home myself.

805
00:35:07,521 --> 00:35:07,881
Also,

806
00:35:08,281 --> 00:35:08,641
Here, take this back.

807
00:35:09,001 --> 00:35:09,961
I’m leaving. Bye.

808
00:35:13,321 --> 00:35:15,241
A man doesn’t even know to walk you home.

809
00:35:15,281 --> 00:35:16,321
So clueless.

810
00:35:29,401 --> 00:35:30,201
What’s wrong?

811
00:35:31,961 --> 00:35:33,961
I don’t like you getting close to other men.

812
00:35:37,321 --> 00:35:39,281
You mean Su Wen?

813
00:35:41,681 --> 00:35:43,481
You don’t trust me, do you?

814
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,240
It’s not that I don’t trust you.

815
00:35:48,161 --> 00:35:48,721
It’s just

816
00:35:49,881 --> 00:35:51,561
I get annoyed when other men look at you.

817
00:35:52,521 --> 00:35:53,361
When you talk to other men,

818
00:35:53,401 --> 00:35:54,601
I get even more upset.

819
00:36:01,121 --> 00:36:02,681
I'm super jealous by nature.

820
00:36:03,441 --> 00:36:05,681
I wish I could be with you
twenty-four hours a day.

821
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:07,080
I won't let any man get close to you.

822
00:36:09,321 --> 00:36:10,881
You're so possessive.

823
00:36:12,121 --> 00:36:14,401
Isn't Jun Lin Tian Xia famous
for being domineering?

824
00:36:16,041 --> 00:36:16,881
Su Wen

825
00:36:17,881 --> 00:36:19,641
I don't mind you giving a lecture there.

826
00:36:20,881 --> 00:36:21,721
But you

827
00:36:23,281 --> 00:36:24,561
have to tell me in advance.

828
00:36:26,641 --> 00:36:27,281
Okay.

829
00:36:27,321 --> 00:36:28,041
I'll do as you say.

830
00:36:49,041 --> 00:36:49,681
Baby.

831
00:36:50,681 --> 00:36:51,401
Let's drink.

832
00:36:53,841 --> 00:36:54,921
What are you looking at?

833
00:36:58,041 --> 00:36:59,361
A game.

834
00:36:59,401 --> 00:37:00,521
I thought you were working.

835
00:37:00,561 --> 00:37:01,961
Turns out you're gaming.

836
00:37:03,401 --> 00:37:04,281
What are you doing?

837
00:37:04,881 --> 00:37:06,201
What am I doing?

838
00:37:07,081 --> 00:37:08,041
Su Wen

839
00:37:08,481 --> 00:37:10,081
Do you want the game or me?

840
00:37:10,641 --> 00:37:11,441
The game.

841
00:37:12,201 --> 00:37:13,161
Say that again.

842
00:37:13,561 --> 00:37:14,801
Ask me ten times,

843
00:37:14,841 --> 00:37:15,841
I'll still choose the game.

844
00:37:20,761 --> 00:37:21,521
Give me the key.

845
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:24,920
You're breaking up with me over a game?

846
00:37:25,561 --> 00:37:26,921
It's not about the game.

847
00:37:27,281 --> 00:37:28,641
It's about respect.

848
00:37:32,921 --> 00:37:33,921
Alright.

849
00:37:34,961 --> 00:37:36,281
I was wrong this time.

850
00:37:36,321 --> 00:37:37,601
I won't do it again.

851
00:37:38,361 --> 00:37:39,881
Don't be mad, okay?

852
00:37:41,681 --> 00:37:42,321
Toward you,

853
00:37:42,961 --> 00:37:44,081
